description: Welcome to this serene corner unit 2-bathroom condo offering 1,223 square feet of thoughtfully designed living space in the heart of South Boston. Perfectly blending comfort and convenience, this home features an open-concept layout ideal for both relaxing and entertaining. The sun-splashed living area flows seamlessly into a modern kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and ample cabinetry. Both bedrooms are generously sized, including a primary suite with a private bath and large closet. Hardwood floors, central A/C, in-unit laundry, and abundant storage complete the interior. Enjoy a shared roof deck with panoramic city views and a dedicated parking space—a rare find in this vibrant neighborhood. Just moments from the Red Line, Seaport, South End, local restaurants, shops, beach and parks, this home offers the ultimate urban lifestyle in one of Boston’s most sought-after areas. Don’t miss the opportunity to make this Southie gem your own!
